      "content": "serotonin syndrome sounds really scary but i feel like i'd notice if something was seriously wrong, like if i was actually in danger? if i just took a low dose for a few days to get through finals, do you think that would be okay? i just really can't make it to a doctor appointment right now with my schedule.",
